CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - How It's Like This - Charles (Teenie) Harris Jr., left, seems to be explaining a strong point to his wife, right, and Adelaide Montgomery and Doris Owens as they enjoy themselves at the Junior Mothers Night picnic at Lovuola's Farm during Frog Week activities. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Charles A. Harris, speaking across picnic table to Adelaide Montgomery, Doris Owens, and wife Beatrice Scott Harris, at Junior Mothers Night picnic at Lovuola's Farm during FROGS week
